captions.english: a small bird with bright yellow breast, belly, and thighs, black tarsus and feet, a black eyering, white wingbars and black coverts, and secondaries
captions.indo: seekor burung kecil dengan dada, perut, dan paha berwarna kuning cerah, tarsus dan kaki hitam, cincin mata hitam, garis sayap putih dan bulu hitam, dan bulu sekunder

captions.english: this bird is orange and black in color, and has a multi colored beak.
captions.indo: burung ini berwarna oranye dan hitam, serta memiliki paruh yang beraneka warna.
